</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p><note id="GUID-2EE2D8D8-CDA6-4668-A8F4-568258C2AB27" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Make sure you hear a clicking sound if you connect the optical fiber connector. 
